{"tid":872213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★劉小麗踩場狙擊選舉主任爆衝突 兩名女保安人員一度高呼非禮","createTime":"2018-10-22T14:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:49:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"460e543a0bd7b307d44ef62e868c08f0ff036630","tid":872213,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181022/photo/bkn-20181022201240640-1022_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181022205616\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181022%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181022201240640-1022_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181022205616&h=f9f2a44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被取消立法會議員資格的自決派劉小麗，聯同泛民主派人士今日(22日)傍晚踩場，狙擊選舉主任。他們在一個活動上拉起橫額、高喊口號，批評選舉主任「可恥」，一度引起混亂，被保安驅趕離場，期間劉小麗與保安員互相拉扯。<br />\n<br />\n被逐離場後，劉小麗一度打算離開，惟經常在社運活動高舉龍獅旗、人稱「美國隊長」的容偉業在場外突然發難，衝前用粗口辱罵保安，並聯同其他示威人士圍堵保安，<span style=\"color: red;\">兩名女保安人員一度高呼非禮。</span><br />\n<br />\n此外，有網媒記者自稱在混亂中被保安打爛眼鏡，要求保安賠償，雙方對罵並發生肢體衝突，其後該名記者報警，有警員到場維持秩序，混亂才告平息，劉小麗和示威人士和平散去。據了解，暫無人受傷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181022/bkn-20181022201240640-1022_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181022%2Fbkn-20181022201240640-1022_00822_001.html&d=ddV51QvMXIqpgBjBDUFDuJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4901209e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181022/bkn-20181022201240640-1022_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"581fc812611d2bcad4576639ea213de2acb00e5c","tid":872213,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9041d46677577aeda0af845ce832381f81c54f","tid":872213,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oge0eXe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3